description:
🗣🧠 #FreeYourMind
.
⏰🐇⏰🐇⏰NO DEALS⏰🐇⏰🐇⏰
.
For so long you thought it couldn’t be true
.
“But I loved their movies how could they do that to a child?”
.
“But he’s such a good musician he wouldn’t ever do something like that?”
.
“I can’t believe that she’s always a good girl on tv”
.
It’s was all right in front of you the whole time.
.
Just like EVERYTHING else
.
This is the cause that will ultimately bring the entire world together, SAVING CHILDREN.
.
Innocent angels that have had their innocence stolen from them by blood sucking demons parading around while you worship them.
.
Hollywood is Bleeding 🩸
.
💡From DARK to LIGHT 💡 
.
We need to put on the full armor of God because this is like nothing the world has faced before, and they won’t go away without a fight.

If you thought what you have witnessed has been shocking buckle up now because they are cornered and will do ANYTHING to survive, even if it means taking us out with them.....
.
THE DEEP STATE IS FALLING
.
WE ARE WINNING THIS WAR
.
Let’s stop marching towards each other in a endless battle of who is the favorite color and let’s unite to go after these sick bastards who are torturing these innocent children for their own sick and twisted gratification.
.
Some of these victims are born into these satanic groups and don’t know anything different, these people are monsters.
.
Let’s save these babies and give them a chance to live their lives the way GOD intended and reach down and grab them all from hell and raise them into the light.
.
We are the voice for the voiceless.
.
#SaveTheChildren #QAnonArmy
#WWG1WGA #TheGreatAwakening #GodWins #GodIsAngry #JudgementDayIsComing #IPromiseYou #DrainTheSwamp
